&lt;a href=&quot;https://cassci.datastax.com/view/Dev/view/krummas/job/krummas-marcuse-9292-dtest/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://cassci.datastax.com/view/Dev/view/krummas/job/krummas-marcuse-9292-dtest/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
